{"tid":1039943,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"冬陰功國","createTime":"2019-02-27T18:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T07:23:21.000Z","uid":113143,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf8ccdb21b7a71ef8c2b1d200ad81f0e7a23748","tid":1039943,"uid":113143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T18:19:48.000Z","msg":"hihi 岩岩玩完pattaya 3日2夜<br />\n<br />\n玩：<br />\n去左flight of the gibbon玩飛索 幾好玩  扮下泰山 9叫下 幾舒暢 不過個人認為唔夠刺激  盛惠6xx港紙(真係唔記得) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnouVgv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnouVgv.jpg&h=32f8ded7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEasykart卡丁車 270cc 睇落好似好慢  揸落識飛  好刺激 全部已經磨到光頭軚  甩尾無難度  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TB6PVjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTB6PVjs.jpg&h=6afaf138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸左4場 每場8分鐘 盛惠451蚊  佢會每場每個圈都計時  最期待的畫面就係攞成績表   <br />\n不過揸4場其實好攰  大家要去就量力而為<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQyVQQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQyVQQx.jpg&h=778ee922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjAUmXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjAUmXd.jpg&h=6d2203b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\npattaya食方面 食左兩間海鮮<br />\n紅姐<br />\nmum aroi<br />\n<br />\n紅姐  華人開 中式煮法  又貴又唔好食 法官大人冇補充 比錢我都唔會再屌 <br />\n<br />\nmum aroi上網睇都好多local去  海鮮都係泰式煮法 網上都一致好評  其實比紅jer搞到好驚有期望又失望   不過呢間真係好有驚喜 海鮮好新鮮  每人都係食左1000泰 250港紙   食到扒係度  我高度推介！！<br />\n(相後補) <br />\n<br />\n今日開始bangkok 5日4夜<br />\n各位巴絲有冇咩好玩好食推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f5bc9e694628edea49a40b6048b0a48ead4602a3","tid":1039943,"uid":217060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T21:01:31.000Z","msg":"Bangkok 我中意食mangotree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf1e3f07bed